cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image generation and manipulation. It also involves the use of neural networks, which makes it relevant to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. As the paper deals with adversarial attacks, it could also be classified under the computer security and cryptography (cs.CR) sub-category. Finally, since the paper proposes a new approach for generating adversaries, it could also be relevant to the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
